Data exploration is an iterative process. It typically involves these steps:

 View the dataset.
 Explore—Get to know the boundaries and shape of your data.
 Refine—Narrow your view to the most important data.
 Save your work.
 Share—Share your view with others.

To explore and visualize your data interactively, use CRM Analytics.
